    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Drop-in faster k-means: same interface as <ref refid="structfaiss_1_1Clustering" kindref="compound">faiss::Clustering</ref>. Per iteration: iter 0: full GEMM over all d dims (vanilla Lloyd&apos;s). iter 1..niter-1: GEMM over front d_prime dims, then ADSampling progressive pruning over PDX-laid trailing dims.</para>
<para>Trains in a randomly-rotated space; centroids are un-rotated before return. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
